OL,5,ETWITCHERS ARE OUT FOR THE COUNT        
OL,7,BTheBinformation gathered by twitchers  
OL,8,Bwill be used by keyEconservation groups
OL,9,Band countryside organisations to see   
OL,10,Bhow the birds fareBin years to come.   
OL,12,BA survey for 1995/6 by the Wetland Bird
OL,13,BSurvey revealed in November and January
OL,14,Bthat there wereE3 million waterfowl    
OL,15,Bregularly using the 1,500 sites.       
OL,17,BFor information on volunteer work write
OL,18,Bto theEBTOBat The Nunnery, Thetford,   
OL,19,BNorfolk IP24 2PU. Or callE01842 750050.
