OL,5,ETWITCHERS ARE OUT FOR THE COUNT        
OL,7,BDid you know that birdwatching is one  
OL,8,Bof Britain's most popular pastimes?    
OL,10,EBRSPB membership has soared to more   
OL,11,  Bthan 1 million, making it Europe's   
OL,12,B  largest conservation charity.        
OL,14,EB67% of us feed garden birds in winter
OL,16,EBA footy game between a Birdwatching  
OL,17, B team and an Isle of Scilly side was  
OL,18,B  cancelled when the twitchers heard of
OL,19,B  a rare sighting in Norfolk and fled! 
